exercise.name: Kneeling Quadriceps Stretch
exercise.description: Kneel on the floor with your right leg forward and left leg back.  With perfect posture, press your hips forward until your feel a stretch in the front of your left thigh.

exercise.name: Butterfly Stretch
exercise.description: Sit with your knees out and soles of your feet together.. Keep a tall torso as you lean your chest forward,, and push your knees apart with your elbows. Breathe deeply.

exercise.name: Arm Sweep Stretch
exercise.description: Laying on your right side with knees at 90 degrees, circle your left arm around the world and then tuck it behind your back.  Retrace the steps to get back to the starting position.

exercise.name: Tin Soldiers
exercise.description: Start tall with your feet together.. Kick one leg straight out in front of you,, while keeping your torso tall and both legs straight.. Snap your heel down,, to finish back underneath you.. Alternate legs..

exercise.name: Hip Cradles
exercise.description: Stand tall and gently pull your knee and ankle up toward your chest, stretching the outside of your hip.

exercise.name: Airplanes
exercise.description: Pivot from the hip of your left leg.  As you see-saw down, keep your upper body and right leg moving as one piece.  Go to parallel and then pull back up.

exercise.name: Bent Over YTW
exercise.description: Hinge over until your upper body is parallel with the ground.  Lift your arms into a Y position and imagine squeezing a pencil between your shoulder blades.  Lower back down and then repeat in a T with arms out to the sides, and finally a W with bent arms.
